column5: Thinking outside the box.  Wiggle wiggle wiggle   Nice one bud.
I tried that   cause I didn't have any dynamite  lol
It was your/our  birthday gift, the  only wiggle we may get.
At least you are fishing! If my daughter stays in Inisfil I may come come up and do some icefishing from the park as I did many years ago. Love  the area in winter.  Loud and clear, me too.
Right on Terry!  Haven't used one of those in years, but they're such lucky little lures though.
